meta_description: Self Adhesive Carpet Protection
description: Self Adhesive Carpet Protection
short_description: The most effective way to temporarily protect synthetic carpets from damage during high traffic times. Carpet Protection Film brand is the choice of professional contractors, home builders and property managers. A tough, 3mil linear low density polyethylene film with a solvent based adhesive applied to one side. The product is highly resistant to tearing and puncturing, stays in place, has a skid resistant surface and is easy to remove.
size_info: PolyTak Carpet Mask Self Adhesive Carpet Protection

meta_description: Environmentally safe surface protection.
description: Environmentally safe surface protection.
short_description: An environmentally friendly, heavy-duty temporary floor protection. It is manufactured with Reinforced Fiber-Flex Technology and protects new and existing floors while allowing moisture and vapors to escape for curing. Designed to protect Wood Floors, Tile, Concrete (including Colored or Stamped), Marble, Stone, Linoleum, Vinyl and many others from damage of foot traffic, hand trucks, fork lifts, scissor lifts etc, during construction and finishing. Roll Size: 38" x 100'(317 sf) Weight (approx): 50 lbs Thinkness (approx): 50 mil Heavy-Duty surface protection Reinforced Fiber-Flex Technology Installs fast and flat 100% Recyclable - green product Reusable Saves time and money from damage, repairs and clean up
size_info: PolyTak Eco-Board - Environmentally Friendly Surface Protection

Floor Mask is a specially formulated 3 mil. self adhesive poly film designed to provide temporary protection for hard surfaces. Use this product during construction, plastering, painting, remodeling, renovations or repairs. Ideal for use on linoleum, ceramic tile, glass, bathtubs, cultured marble, counter tops and other surfaces. To protect finished hardwood floors use Floorliner (page 7) or Floor Mask Non-Adhesive below.

meta_title: Floor Mask Non-Adhesive Floor Protection Film
short_description: Protecting Hardwood floors and maintaining a cleaner, safer work environment. The Floor Mask Non-Adhesive has 100% non-woven runners and a non-skid backing which makes it stay put in short lengths and can be trimmed to fit any area. The Floor Mask Non-Adhesive is durable, reusable and will not tear or disintegrate. Is is also versatile, highly absorbent and easy to use.

short_description: Floorliner is comprised of non-woven synthetic fibers that have a polyethylene topside and a light tack adhesive on the back. These features protect the surface from liquid spills and unsure slip resistance once applied to the surface. Flootliner is reusable and may be left in place for up to 120 days and is safe for tile and other non-porous surfaces. This product can also be used on linoleum, ceramic tile, flass tiles, bathtubs, cultured marble, counter tops and other hard surfaces.
summary: CAUTION: Do not use on newly laid clay tiles and porous stone plates because rising moisture can not escape. The adhesive used with hardwood floor installation MUST be cured before application of Floorliner because moisture can not escape. Site finished floors must be properly prepared.

meta_description: Clean room mats for High Tech, Industrial and Abatement.
description: Clean room mats for High Tech, Industrial and Abatement.
short_description: Placing this high tech product in traffic areas and main entrances will help protect and extend the life of floor finishes, carpets, and furnishings. Reduces maintenance and cleaning costs by significantly decreasing the amount of dirt contamination. The adhesive coated film on top effectively removes dirt from shoes and equipment wheels. As foot traffic or wheels pass over the surface of the mat, the non-transferring adhesive locks onto the dirt and captures it. When the exposed layer is completely used, simply peel it off to expose the next clean layer. Commonly used in clean room applications. Two styles available; one with a PVC frame with non-skid backing and the other without a frame, and an adhesice backing to adhere to placement surface.
